  "body": "#### System information\r\nGeth\r\nVersion: 1.9.11-stable\r\nGit Commit: 6a62fe399b68ab9e3625ef5e7900394f389adc3a\r\nArchitecture: amd64\r\nProtocol Versions: [65 64 63]\r\nGo Version: go1.13.8\r\nOperating System: linux\r\nGOPATH=\r\nGOROOT=/build/ethereum-2t6lYR/.go\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\nThe following two do the same\r\n--miner.gasprice 0\r\n\r\n[Eth.Miner]\r\nGasPrice = 0\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\nWhen gasprice is specified in toml file, transaction with gasprice of 0 is not propagated.\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\nBuild a private clique with two miner and non-miner nodes.\r\nChange only the above options and send transactions with gasprice of 0 to non-miners.\r\n",
