    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I will close this issue now. \r\n\r\nThere are two minimal gasprice settings in Geth, one is `miner.gasprice` which specifies the minimal acceptable price for mining. Another one is `txpool.pricelimit` which specifies the minimal acceptable price for \"propagation\".\r\n\r\nZero price transactions won't be propagated through the network. So in your case the transaction won't arrive the miner's node even you change the `miner.gasprice`.",
